<br>
1. Burst damage? (no--wizzie)<br>
2. Long term damage in group? (maybe but not by much and definitely not if the group has a charmed pet)<br>
3. Long term damage on raids? (I'd give that title necros/rogues/ and even wizzies in some situations depending on resists and the target--this is on a single mob that takes say 5 min to kill)<br>
4. Soloing for AA? (Enchanter/Necros/druids/wizzies)<br>
5. Soloing large mobs? (Enchanters/Necros/Shaman)<br>
6. Versatility? (enchanter/druid/shaman/hell in necros)<br>
7. Survivability during bad times? (druid/necro)<br>
<br>
I don't see us being above any class when measured reasonably.  What we are good at is DoT in both raids and exp with small bits of utlity.  But way overpowered?  come on.<br>
<br>
I'm happy with my mage and what he can do, but we are hardly overpowered.  For the first time in a while we are where we should be. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jayteebushwacker>Jaytee Bushwacker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Summoner Da'FoH</span><br>  Posts: 1385<br> <font color=#333333>(1/6/03 8:38:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=443.topic&index=26>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Overpowered?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>And any mage who asks to keep it is a hypocrite. All the time we complained about being unbalanced. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
